<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer2760896962736681918">Grecian is the author of several bestselling thrillers, including THE SAINT OF WOLVES AND BUTCHERS, and five novels featuring Scotland Yard&apos;s Murder Squad: THE YARD, THE BLACK COUNTRY, THE DEVIL&apos;S WORKSHOP, THE HARVEST MAN, and LOST AND GONE FOREVER, plus the original Murder Squad ebook, THE BLUE GIRL.<br/><br/>He also created the six-volume graphic novel series PROOF, and the two-part graphic novel RASPUTI</span>
  <span id="freeText2760896962736681918" style="display:none">Grecian is the author of several bestselling thrillers, including THE SAINT OF WOLVES AND BUTCHERS, and five novels featuring Scotland Yard's Murder Squad: THE YARD, THE BLACK COUNTRY, THE DEVIL'S WORKSHOP, THE HARVEST MAN, and LOST AND GONE FOREVER, plus the original Murder Squad ebook, THE BLUE GIRL.<br /><br />He also created the six-volume graphic novel series PROOF, and the two-part graphic novel RASPUTIN.<br /><br />He currently lives in the American Midwest with his wife and son. And a dog. And a tarantula.</span>
